Sally Mansfield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sally_Mansfield 0 Marie Mahder (December 13, 1920 – January 28, 2001), best known by her stage name Sally Mansfield, was an American television character actress; she also had a few small roles in feature films including one with Dean Martin and Jerry Lewis.
